      <description>&lt;section id="overview" data-observe="true"                         class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_175px] sm-opaque1 py-5 px-5 lg:py-10 lg:px-10 pt-24 lg:pt-10 mb-0 lg:mb-10"&gt;                          &lt;div class=""&gt;                             &lt;h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide uppercase text-cardforeground"&gt;                                 Overview                                                               &lt;/h2&gt;                              &lt;div                                 class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 pr-8 mt-8 overview-icons xl:gap-6 xl:grid-cols-2 text-cardforeground"&gt;                                   &lt;div class="release-date"&gt;                                     &lt;div class="flex items-center justify-center min-w-0 gap-x-6"&gt;                                         &lt;div&gt;&lt;i class="fa-light fa-headphones"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;                                         &lt;div class="flex-auto min-w-0"&gt;                                             &lt;p                                                 class="font-serif text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-subheader"&gt;                                                 Releasing on                                             &lt;/p&gt;                                             &lt;p class="text-sm"&gt;                                                 Thursday, August 14, 2025                                            &lt;/p&gt;                                         &lt;/div&gt;                                     &lt;/div&gt;                                 &lt;/div&gt;                                                                  &lt;div class="range"&gt;                                     &lt;div class="flex items-center justify-center min-w-0 gap-x-6"&gt;                                         &lt;div&gt;&lt;i class="fa-kit fa-worlds-of-doctor-who"&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;            